  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "We need the following commands:\r\n\r\n### For the handshake\r\n\r\n- `Status`: Exchange protocol version, network id, and head hash\r\n\r\n### For chain syncing\r\n\r\n- `GetBeaconBlock`: Get a specific block by hash or number\r\n- `BeaconBlock`: Reply with a requested block\r\n\r\n### For building the chain\r\n\r\n- `BeaconBlock`: Same command as above, but sent with out request\r\n- `AttestationRecord`: Send attestations\r\n\r\n### What we ignore for now to keep it simple\r\n\r\n- Requesting/sending multiple blocks\r\n- State syncing\r\n- `SpecialRecord`s",
